00:35:50.740 --> 00:35:53.260
our fierceness
and our gentleness

00:35:53.260 --> 00:35:56.950
in order to operate
in a fully human way.

00:35:56.950 --> 00:35:57.920
I really liked that.

00:35:57.920 --> 00:35:59.970
And so every sort
of moment of my life

00:35:59.970 --> 00:36:02.680
that I've had some sort of big
realization about the person I

00:36:02.680 --> 00:36:05.350
