00:36:10.342 --> 00:36:11.800
You know, time
isn't linear anyway.

00:36:11.800 --> 00:36:12.508
We all know that.

00:36:12.508 --> 00:36:14.950
So how do we mark our
lives in a way that

00:36:14.950 --> 00:36:17.320
contains them in some way and
there's a story behind it.

00:36:17.320 --> 00:36:21.270
The best part about writing this
book, really, was that like,

00:36:21.270 --> 00:36:23.790
