my identity in a world that

00:36:23.790 --> 00:36:25.460
didn't always
understand it, but also

00:36:25.460 --> 00:36:28.890
to assert my understanding of
just the way life operates.

00:36:28.890 --> 00:36:31.970
It's a book that really--
time is kind of like always

00:36:31.970 --> 00:36:33.319
in a vortex.

00:36:33.319 --> 00:36:35.610
And I think that's how memory
works and how life works.

00:36:35.610 --> 00:36:38.450
We are organized much more
thematically than we think

00:36:38.450 --> 00:36:41.920
and much less in a
way that's linear.

00:36:41.920 --> 00:36:44.490
It's less spatial,
it's more thematic.

00:36:44.490 --> 00:36:46.950
So in a lot of ways,
I think that's just

00:36:46.950 --> 00:36:49.720
tattooing, writing a
book, being an artist

00:36:49.720 --> 00:36:52.760
in any way is about being
able to operate in that realm.

